{"sn2.18:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.18 ","sn2.18:0.2":"2. Anathapindikavagga ","sn2.18:0.3":"Kakudhasutta ","sn2.18:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn2.18:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava sakete viharati anjanavane migadaye. ","sn2.18:1.3":"Atha kho kakudho devaputto abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanno kevalakappam anjanavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. Ekamantam thito kho kakudho devaputto bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn2.18:1.4":"“nandasi, samana”ti? ","sn2.18:1.5":"“Kim laddha, avuso”ti? ","sn2.18:1.6":"“Tena hi, samana, socasi”ti? ","sn2.18:1.7":"“Kim jiyittha, avuso”ti? ","sn2.18:1.8":"“Tena hi, samana, neva nandasi na ca socasi”ti? ","sn2.18:1.9":"“Evamavuso”ti. ","sn2.18:2.1":"“Kacci tvam anagho bhikkhu, ","sn2.18:2.2":"kacci nandi na vijjati; ","sn2.18:2.3":"Kacci tam ekamasinam, ","sn2.18:2.4":"arati nabhikirati”ti. ","sn2.18:3.1":"“Anagho ve aham yakkha, ","sn2.18:3.2":"atho nandi na vijjati; ","sn2.18:3.3":"Atho mam ekamasinam, ","sn2.18:3.4":"arati nabhikirati”ti. ","sn2.18:4.1":"“Katham tvam anagho bhikkhu, ","sn2.18:4.2":"katham nandi na vijjati; ","sn2.18:4.3":"Katham tam ekamasinam, ","sn2.18:4.4":"arati nabhikirati”ti. ","sn2.18:5.1":"“Aghajatassa ve nandi, ","sn2.18:5.2":"nandijatassa ve agham; ","sn2.18:5.3":"Anandi anagho bhikkhu, ","sn2.18:5.4":"evam janahi avuso”ti. ","sn2.18:6.1":"“Cirassam vata passami, ","sn2.18:6.2":"brahmanam parinibbutam; ","sn2.18:6.3":"Anandim anagham bhikkhum, ","sn2.18:6.4":"tinnam loke visattikan”ti. "}